\
Future runs with --golden flag:\
  - Load golden EvalResult for each payload\
  - Compare current JudgeResults against golden JudgeResults\
  - A criterion that passed in golden but fails now = REGRESSION\
  - A criterion that failed in golden but passes now = IMPROVEMENT\
  - Report includes regression_vs_golden summary\
